Odyssea.io is one the first, and largest, Marketplaces dedicated to luxury goods tokenization. It is built on the Datachain Foundation Infrastructure. The platform allows everyone to discover, collect, buy, sell luxury goods and their digital twins of in the form of NFTs.

Join our community of craftsmens, showcase

Introducing Passive Income royalties
Now premium craftsman and luxury good makers can
perceive perpetual royalties from the future sales of
their creation, thus, getting rewarded for their work.

Designed To Enhance Trust And Value
Tangible assets’ digital twins are encapsulated in NFTs
to create Non-Forgeable Assets. NFA enable on-chain
transaction of physical goods creating a tamper-proof
record of each tokenized asset’s history.
Transforming Luxury and Iconic Brands Into Non-Forgeable Assets. Bridging the gap between metaverses ecosystem and traditional economy.
